data.description: Be ready to move right in! 1 Story, gorgeous Home that is extremely well maintained.  Spacious , open Floor Plan along with 3 Bedrooms and 2 Full Bathrooms.  Ideal for entertaining with a Family Room directly off the Kitchen. Tons of light throughout the Home with a relaxing enclosed patio, where you can enjoy the weather on a beautiful So. Florida day. Newer HVAC, newer Washer & Dryer, and newer Major Appliances.  Boca Country Club is located in the heart of luxurious Boca Raton, w/  easy access to I-95 and other major highways. HOA includes: Gated and Manned Security, Cable, Roof Washing, Exterior Painting. The best shopping and restaurants just minutes from the Community. NO MEMBERSHIP and an AFFORDABLE HOA...Best and Top rated schools just minutes away. Come and see it for yourself!
